isual cue for when to add the next ladle of broth.', 2, '2026-04-06 10:45:00'),
(44, 13, 2, '{\"title\":\"Mushroom Risotto\",\"preparationTime\":40,\"servings\":4,\"instructions\":\"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Saute onion and garlic in butter over medium heat.\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Add mushrooms and cook until soft and golden.\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Add rice and stir 1 min to toast lightly.\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Deglaze with wine and stir until absorbed.\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Add broth one ladle at a time over medium-low heat, waiting until each ladle is fully absorbed before adding the next.\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Finish with grated cheese, adjust seasoning, and serve immediately.\\\"}]\",\"notes\":\"Keep the broth warm in a separate pot while cooking - adding cold broth stops the cooking process and results in uneven texture. Stir constantly during the final 10 minutes.\",\"description\":\"Creamy Arborio-style rice slowly cooked with mushrooms, white wine, and chicken broth, finished with grated kashkaval. Rich and deeply savory.\",\"products\":[{\"productName\":\"Rice\",\"position\":1,\"quantity\":300.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"g\"},{\"productName\":\"Mushrooms\",\"position\":2,\"quantity\":400.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"g\"},{\"productName\":\"Chicken broth\",\"position\":3,\"quantity\":1000.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"ml\"},{\"productName\":\"White wine (for cooking)\",\"position\":4,\"quantity\":100.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"ml\"},{\"productName\":\"Onions\",\"position\":5,\"quantity\":1.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"pcs\"},{\"productName\":\"Garlic\",\"position\":6,\"quantity\":2.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"pcs\"},{\"productName\":\"Butter\",\"position\":7,\"quantity\":50.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"g\"},{\"productName\":\"Kashkaval (Yellow cheese)\",\"position\":8,\"quantity\":60.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"g\"},{\"productName\":\"Salt\",\"position\":9,\"quantity\":6.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"g\"},{\"productName\":\"Black pepper (ground)\",\"position\":10,\"quantity\":3.000,\"unitAbbreviation\":\"g\"}],\"categories\":[{\"category\":\"Main Dishes\"},{\"category\":\"Vegetarian & Vegan\"}]}', NULL, 1, '2026-04-08 14:20:00'),
